sentences.sentence: After menopause, women start to display similar body morphologies as men.
sentences.translation: 女性在绝经以后，开始显现出与男性类似的身体形态特征来。

sentences.sentence: There are different fibril morphologies on the different zones of injection - molded samples.
sentences.translation: 在注塑成型样品的不同区域，纤维的形态也不尽相同。

sentences.sentence: These seemingly random objects are essential to helping us formulate complex morphologies into tangible suppositions.
sentences.translation: 这些看似随意摆放的物品对于帮助我们将复杂的形态转化为有形的推测起到了非常关键的作用。
